      "text": "what need to be done before reproducing architectures\n ? :",
      "fontSize": 28.104675292968757,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "what need to be done before reproducing architectures\n ? :",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ot7FrvOBE60Zw3zy_-AcH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -222.39701516287664,
      "y": -87.26365879603796,
      "width": 813.439208984375,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ag",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1481695421,
      "version": 954,
      "versionNonce": 501857715,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783364956067,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "HOW : \n-Procedural mode for now , maybe switching in oop in the future\n-USING: Numpy only\nwhat need to be built :  \n-  Implementation of different objective function MSE,CEL\n- Implementation of well known heuristics ( activation functions ) : Relu,Sigmoid,ect\n- Implementing the derivatives of the different activation function\n- Implementing the backward pass engine ! \n\nhaving those tools I will be able to  implement different architectures \nthe backward engine remain the core,critical algorithm to implement ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "HOW : \n-Procedural mode for now , maybe switching in oop in the future\n-USING: Numpy only\nwhat need to be built :  \n-  Implementation of different objective function MSE,CEL\n- Implementation of well known heuristics ( activation functions ) : Relu,Sigmoid,ect\n- Implementing the derivatives of the different activation function\n- Implementing the backward pass engine ! \n\nhaving those tools I will be able to  implement different architectures \nthe backward engine remain the core,critical algorithm to implement ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
