      "updated": 1783364973388,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "x --> mlp_function ---> heuristic_function\n--> loss\na function is a python object that cannot\nstore data and thus our parameter thats\nwhy\noop is actually more common here a  cache\nwould be needed to store internal\nrepresentations\nand weights.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "x --> mlp_function ---> heuristic_function\n--> loss\na function is a python object that cannot\nstore data and thus our parameter thats why\noop is actually more common here a  cache\nwould be needed to store internal representations\nand weights.",
